723349f-a.title: Manhattan: South Street - Gouverneur Slip
723349f-a.text:
369 South Street, west of the N.W. corner of Gouverneur Slip.
March 23, 1937.
723349f-a.folder: South Street & Gouverneur Slip, Manhattan, NY

723350f-b.title: Manhattan: South Street - Gouverneur Slip
723350f-b.text:
South Street, east from Gouverneur Slip, showing a small park in the foreground and industrial buildings beyond. These will be removed to provide for the marginal East River Drive. Gouverneur Hospital at the left, facing on Front Street, will then be
open to view.
1: March 23, 1937
2: Sept. 18, 1939
P. L. Sperr
